{"tid":546801,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[無圖] 啱啱7:30分係太子轉車個男仔好靚仔","createTime":"2018-02-01T00:07:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-05T07:03:01.000Z","uid":64345,"like":10,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"00cb49e467c8ff81a1dbf20c5d49d28751cb8f0e","tid":546801,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T00:07:25.000Z","msg":"7:29分係深水埗向中環方向車頭上車就見到你啦。<br />\n好耐都無見過你啦。之前都係7點3~4個字就撞到你。<br />\n今日你着藍色連帽羽絨，黑白格頸巾，揹返同一個黑色背囊。見你係車廂都要用頂帽笠頭同呻鼻，係咪凍親呀。<br />\n不過你副文青眼鏡依然好sharp，呢個亦係我第一次留意到你的原因。<br />\n7:33分你係九龍塘落車轉東鐵線，唔知你係轉去邊呢？咁早唔似大學生返學。<br />\n<br />\n好想識你呀，我想以後多啲機會撞到你。<br />\n<br />\n利申︰gay"},{"pid":"007c1384bb648ce1354d77978e3f387826a38073","tid":546801,"uid":120093,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T00:08:23.000Z","msg":"想互射?"},{"pid":"842f82cead8eefc58334b94d420d9009eb905d60","tid":546801,"uid":21423,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T00:09:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2e220911aa29ae618d1906215b7994cdb12a031d","tid":546801,"uid":64345,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"007c1384bb648ce1354d77978e3f387826a38073","tid":546801,"uid":120093,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T00:08:23.000Z","msg":"想互射?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T00:10:52.000Z","msg":"想聽吓佢把聲。應該會係低音得黎又好有魅力嗰類<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8441e977032ea4fd3cf279f3d7d080f428d20435","tid":546801,"uid":64345,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"842f82cead8eefc58334b94d420d9009eb905d60","tid":546801,"uid":21423,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T00:09:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T00:11:55.000Z","msg":"地鐵咁迫，影唔撚到相。絕對唔核突，好襯。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/fac